<sect1 id="dir_9cbb4b4cfd398af02a68f2645b2e9ca6_1autotoc_md236">
<title>helios::engine::mechanics::scoring</title><para>Score management and tracking system for game mechanics.</para>
<para>This module provides components, systems, and infrastructure for tracking and managing scores in the helios engine. It supports multiple score pools (e.g., per-player), score types (e.g., kill rewards), and integrates with the combat and UI systems.</para>
</sect1>
