<sect1 id="dir_9cbb4b4cfd398af02a68f2645b2e9ca6_1autotoc_md239">
<title>Architecture</title><para>The scoring system follows a command-based architecture:</para>
<para>1. <bold>Combat events</bold> trigger <computeroutput>UpdateScoreCommand</computeroutput> via <computeroutput>CombatScoringSystem</computeroutput> 2. <bold>Commands</bold> are dispatched to <computeroutput>ScorePoolManager</computeroutput> via <computeroutput>ScoreCommandDispatcher</computeroutput> 3. <bold>Scores</bold> are accumulated in <computeroutput>ScorePool</computeroutput> instances 4. <bold>UI</bold> observes pools via <computeroutput>ScoreObserverComponent</computeroutput> + <computeroutput>ScoreObserverSystem</computeroutput></para>
<para><hruler/>
